song_name: I Don t Wanna Kiss You Goodnight
lyrics:
Ohhhh

I can't belive the night is gone, Oh yeah.
And now it's time to take you home.
Girl as I hold your hand and walk you to your door,
Suddenly there's enough of silence.
Both of us stairing at the floor.

(Chorus)
Cause I don't wanna kiss you goodnight
If a kiss means this night is over
I don't wanna have to say goodbye
No no no
Girl don't leave me standing at your door
When this night could  lead to so much more
I wanna hold you
I wanna touch you
So when I kiss you
Don't wanna kiss you good night

I use to see you in my dreams (hoping one day they come true)
And then you gave yourself to me
But now that I'm standing here
And I'm hoping that I'm not just a fool in  your eyes.
Don't wanna leave you hear
I wanna come inside and kiss you where you like it.

Chorus
Cause I don't wanna kiss you goodnight
If a kiss means this night is over
I don't wanna have to say goodbye
No no no
Girl don't leave me standing at your door
When this night could  lead to so much more
I wanna hold you
I wanna touch you
So when I kiss you
Don't wanna kiss you good night

I wish this night could be endless
Baby feeling your skin on my skin
I take my time to make you breathless
Girl we can do it again and again

Chorus (2x)
